
# UI Components (shadcn/ui)

## Available Components
Located in `src/components/ui/`:
- `button.tsx` - Button component with variants
- `card.tsx` - Card container component  
- `table.tsx` - Data table component
- `tabs.tsx` - Tab navigation component
- `dialog.tsx` - Modal dialog component
- `dropdown-menu.tsx` - Dropdown menu component
- `input.tsx` - Form input component
- `select.tsx` - Select dropdown component
- `badge.tsx` - Badge/tag component
- `alert.tsx` - Alert/notification component
- `progress.tsx` - Progress bar component
- `label.tsx` - Form label component

## Usage Patterns
- Import from `@/components/ui/component-name`
- Use proper TypeScript props interfaces
- Follow shadcn/ui documentation for props and variants

## Customization
- Components use CSS variables for theming
- Extend with additional variants using `class-variance-authority`
- Use `cn()` utility from [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts) for conditional classes

## Component Configuration
- Configuration in [components.json](mdc:components.json)
- Style: "new-york"
- Icons: Lucide React
- CSS Variables enabled for theming

## Common Patterns
```tsx
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '@/components/ui/card'

// Button variants: default, destructive, outline, secondary, ghost, link
<Button variant="outline" size="sm">Click me</Button>

// Card structure
<Card>
  <CardHeader>
    <CardTitle>Title</CardTitle>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    Content here
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```

